      "say": "半人馬對艦隊中所有人都稱呼前輩的事，逐漸成為了話題。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "嗯…？為什麼對所有人都用“前輩”稱呼嗎？…指揮官，你知道我是戰後出生的對吧。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "bgm": "story-2",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "當時，因為戰爭結束的關係，我們這一級面臨著被取消的風險。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "後來幾經坎坷，我們才終於得以降生。",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "不過因為戰爭已經結束，我們即使降生了，也沒有體驗過前輩們那種波瀾壯闊的生活。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "如果說不嚮往，那我一定是在否定自己的價值。",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "半人馬淡淡地訴說著。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "不過，不只是這樣的。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "指揮官，我的生涯是在和平之中度過的，我沒有體會過戰爭的傷痛。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "但我在了解前輩們事蹟的同時，也明白了戰爭是什麼樣的東西。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "那絕不是未曾體驗過其殘酷的我，能夠輕率地掛在嘴邊的東西。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "所以，我才更加憧憬和尊敬那些參與過那場戰爭，並且將其終結的前輩們",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "說實在的，光是“前輩”兩個字，完全無法表達我對各位的敬意呢。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "半人馬看來也是自己深思熟慮過的。",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "不過，確實，要是我的堅持給各位添麻煩了那就本末倒置了。",
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 206040,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 3,
      "say": "我會和大家商量的，如果有前輩覺得困擾，那我就克服一下，從行動上體現我對大家的尊敬好了~",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
